title: Kaffe O
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Raw, Juice bar, Take-out, Bakery, Nordic , Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A Nordic inspired coffee shop serving 100% vegetarian soups, stews and salads, some of which are vegan. Also offers a wide range of breakfast, lunch and gluten free baked goods. Always offers vegan dishes made with fresh and whole foods. Drinks include juices and smoothies.
